    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们仨是军团战争的十年脑残粉，有天脑子一热就搞了个工作室，经过四个月的摸索，我们用『CliCli』做出了《军团保卫战》，大家如果对游戏感兴趣的话，都欢迎加我们的Q群：920024164，一起聊天吐槽，或者给我们提提优化建议，我们主打一个听劝！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/31d0f4561d01873fb1141b96597f4e90.poster.avif?t=1761602401\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/31d0f4561d01873fb1141b96597f4e90.webm?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/31d0f4561d01873fb1141b96597f4e90.mp4?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法创新，对抗升级</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物与真人对手交替出现，29个英雄与45种佣兵任你选择。正面硬刚或隐秘偷袭，皆在你一念之间，保护国王并击败敌方，体验无与伦比的智斗爽感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/5ee56e23679ca6d15964c33c7da5994d.poster.avif?t=1761602401\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/5ee56e23679ca6d15964c33c7da5994d.webm?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/5ee56e23679ca6d15964c33c7da5994d.mp4?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>英雄激战，胜者为王</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每到3的倍数回合，即可解锁紧张刺激的3v3捉对厮杀战，18回合更有KOF拳皇模式，玩家轮番上阵打擂，凭借智慧与技巧争夺全场最佳，感受搏击的热血与快感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/3b1c07b81b1e0c7ddfb28c0254173329.poster.avif?t=1761602401\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/3b1c07b81b1e0c7ddfb28c0254173329.webm?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/3b1c07b81b1e0c7ddfb28c0254173329.mp4?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无尽肉鸽，单手爽玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的随机事件与上百种祝福让你每局都有全新体验！灵活运用策略应对未知挑战，享受单手操作带来的对战乐趣，轻松收获爽快竞技体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/9a8c1e62243e4a939df4a9c2934dc99a.poster.avif?t=1761602401\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/9a8c1e62243e4a939df4a9c2934dc99a.webm?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/9a8c1e62243e4a939df4a9c2934dc99a.mp4?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>海量佣兵，灵活搭配</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45种个性佣兵，涵盖肉盾、输出、辅助等多种能力，灵活调整阵形充分发挥佣兵特长，弥补英雄不足，抗住每一波进攻，感受战斗策略的无尽爽感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/c92568b43104f1dc62fff7a1ae1bd50b.poster.avif?t=1761602401\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/c92568b43104f1dc62fff7a1ae1bd50b.webm?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338570/extras/c92568b43104f1dc62fff7a1ae1bd50b.mp4?t=1761602401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
